import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { vitalsAPI } from '../../api/endpoints'; const ReadOnlyConsultationView = ({ consultation, onClose }) => { const [vitals, setVitals] = useState(null); useEffect(() => { fetchVitals(); }, []); const fetchVitals = async () => { try { const response = await vitalsAPI.getLatestVitals(consultation.patient_id); setVitals(response.data); } catch (error) { console.error('Error fetching vitals:', error); } }; const getEyeData = () => { try { if (consultation.tests) { return JSON.parse(consultation.tests); } } catch (error) { console.error('Error parsing eye data:', error); } // Fallback to parsing symptoms if tests field is empty const rightEyeMatch = (consultation.symptoms || '').match(/Right Eye: VA ([^,]*), Cornea ([^.]*)/); const leftEyeMatch = (consultation.symptoms || '').match(/Left Eye: VA ([^,]*), Cornea ([^.]*)/); return { rightEye: { visualAcuity: rightEyeMatch ? rightEyeMatch[1] : 'Not recorded', cornea: rightEyeMatch ? rightEyeMatch[2] : 'Not recorded', lens: 'Not recorded', retina: 'Not recorded', intraocularPressure: 'Not recorded', refraction: 'Not recorded' }, leftEye: { visualAcuity: leftEyeMatch ? leftEyeMatch[1] : 'Not recorded', cornea: leftEyeMatch ? leftEyeMatch[2] : 'Not recorded', lens: 'Not recorded', retina: 'Not recorded', intraocularPressure: 'Not recorded', refraction: 'Not recorded' } }; }; const eyeData = getEyeData(); return (

); }; export default ReadOnlyConsultationView;
